  <brief_title>Dexmedetomidine and Bupivacaine With Bupivacaine in Ultrasonography Guided Fascia Iliaca Compartment Block in Adults</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparison of Dexmedetomidine and Bupivacaine With Bupivacaine Alone on the Quality of Ultrasonography Guided Fascia Iliaca Compartment Block in Adults Undergoing Femur Fracture Fixation Surgery</official_title>
  <sponsors>
