  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Few studies have reported the efficacy of adding dexmedetomidine to bupivacain for fascia
      illiaca compartment black. Comparison of dexmedetomidine and bupivacaine with bupivacaine
      alone on the quality of ultrasonography guided fascia iliaca compartment block in adults
      undergoing femur fracture fixation surgery at 2014.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
